\DOC hol_pathname

\TYPE {hol_pathname : (void -> string)}

\SYNOPSIS
Returns the absolute pathname to the hol system directory.

\DESCRIBE
Evaluating {hol_pathname()} returns a string giving the absolute pathname
to the directory in which the HOL system is resident.

\FAILURE
Never fails.

\EXAMPLE
{
#hol_pathname();;
`/usr/groups/hol/HOL2/sun4_sos` : string
}
\SEEALSO
library_pathname.

\ENDDOC
